AllPrintings.description: All cards, including all printings and variations, categorized by set.

AllPrintingsCSVFiles.description: A directory of .csv files containing all data from AllPrintings.json.

AllPrices.description: All prices of cards in various formats.

AllSetFiles.description: Each individual set file in a directory, compressed.

AllCards.description: Every card as a unique "atomic" object. May also be outputted as every card in a specific set. Some data properties will be omitted if they have differing examples from set to set.

CardTypes.description: Every card type of any type of card.

CompiledList.description: All possible compiled outputs from MTGJSON, such as, AllPrintings, AllCards, etc.

DeckLists.description: All possible compiled pre-constructed deck outputs from MTGJSON.

Keywords.description: List of all keywords used on Magic cards.

LegacyCards.description: All cards, restricted to cards legal in the Legacy format.

LegacyPrintings.description: All sets, restricted to sets legal in the Legacy format.

PauperCards.description: All cards, restricted to cards legal in the Pauper format.

PioneerCards.description: All cards, restricted to cards legal in the Pioneer format.

PioneerPrintings.description: All sets, restricted to sets legal in the Pioneer format.

ModernCards.description: All cards, restricted to cards legal in the Modern format.

ModernPrintings.description: All sets, restricted to sets legal in the Modern format.

SetList.description: List of codes, names and release dates of all sets.

StandardCards.description: All cards, restricted to cards legal in the Standard format.

StandardPrintings.description: All sets, restricted to sets legal in the Standard format.

version.description: Metadata object has {{external:ISO-8601$https://www.iso.org/iso-8601-date-and-time-format.html}} dates for latest build and prices, and version properties of this MTGJSON release.

VintagePrintings.description: All sets, restricted to sets legal in the Vintage format.
